                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1r: Prayer of the seven hours. When you say: "In the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, one God", I bow once, while you are saying: "O Lord, have compassion upon us. O Lord, have compassion upon us. O Lord, bless us. O Lord. Bless us, Amen. Hallelujah." You bow...</q>
                           Incomplete; some passages are erased.
